Thank you for signing up to participate in SONA Study 465!
During this study, please focus on the experiment and refrain from activities such as:

- Switching to other tabs on your browser (this will be monitored via the experiment)
- Using your mobile phone/cell phone
- Communicating with others

This way, you are helping to provide data that is useful for psychological research. We thank you for your cooperation!
